566
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:31,660
Are you okay?

567
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:32,700
Must've worn you out.

568
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:33,620
Not at all.

569
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,700
It's good to have a son.

570
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:36,540
I'm definitely not getting tired.

571
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:37,750
Slowly.

572
00:37:37,870 --> 00:37:38,500
Alright.

573
00:37:38,700 --> 00:37:39,830
I'll take these two bags.

574
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:41,100
You push your mom.

575
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:41,830
Be careful.

576
00:37:41,830 --> 00:37:42,620
Okay. I'll do it.

577
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:43,260
I'll take it.

578
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,700
I'll come back for the bags later.

579
00:37:44,740 --> 00:37:45,300
I'll take it.

580
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:46,990
Alright.

581
00:37:49,020 --> 00:37:50,310
Mom, you're discharged now.

582
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:58,540
There is a little bumpy here.

583
00:37:58,540 --> 00:37:59,350
It's fine.

584
00:38:01,990 --> 00:38:03,580
Take good care of your mom.

585
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:04,140
Okay.

586
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:04,980
If anything comes up,

587
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:06,350
- just let us know.
- Yes, let us know.

588
00:38:06,350 --> 00:38:08,870
Hao, we've been waiting
for you to come home.

589
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:09,990
My husband said

590
00:38:10,060 --> 00:38:12,310
if you need anything, just let us know.

591
00:38:14,870 --> 00:38:15,870
Thank you.

592
00:38:16,270 --> 00:38:17,580
And thank Dr. Li as well.

593
00:38:18,390 --> 00:38:20,700
We're all family. No need to thank me.

594
00:38:20,750 --> 00:38:22,470
Hao, hurry up and go upstairs to rest.

595
00:38:22,470 --> 00:38:23,830
Yes. Come, I'll carry you.

596
00:38:23,950 --> 00:38:24,910
I'll do it.

597
00:38:24,910 --> 00:38:26,500
Let me do it.

598
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,160
You won't be able to carry me.

599
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,000
I can.

600
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,470
Song Hang.

601
00:38:29,470 --> 00:38:30,350
Don't worry. Come on.

602
00:38:30,350 --> 00:38:30,950
Slowly, slowly.

603
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,140
One, two, three.

604
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:33,790
Slowly, slowly.

605
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:34,950
Watch the steps.

606
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:35,750
Be careful.

607
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:36,910
I'll help you pack up.

608
00:38:36,910 --> 00:38:37,220
No, no.

609
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:38,500
It's fine, I'll do it myself.

610
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:39,220
I'll do it myself.

611
00:38:39,220 --> 00:38:40,220
It's nothing, really.

612
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:41,620
Hurry up and go home.

613
00:38:41,620 --> 00:38:42,580
You've worked hard.

614
00:38:43,390 --> 00:38:44,580
Mom, lean on the sofa.

615
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:48,540
This is quite heavy.

616
00:38:49,990 --> 00:38:50,870
Where's Mrs. Li?

617
00:38:50,870 --> 00:38:51,950
I let her go back already.

618
00:38:54,790 --> 00:38:55,750
Are you tired?

619
00:38:55,790 --> 00:38:56,470
I'm fine.

620
00:38:57,680 --> 00:39:00,140
Hang, how about we switch
to a first-floor apartment?

621
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:01,990
With me having to go up
and down every day,

622
00:39:01,990 --> 00:39:03,080
won't that wear you all out?

623
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:04,310
Mom, don't worry.

624
00:39:04,310 --> 00:39:05,700
After transferring, I'll go with Dad

625
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:06,980
to take turns taking care of you.

626
00:39:08,060 --> 00:39:08,830
Transfer schools?

627
00:39:09,950 --> 00:39:10,910
Why would you transfer?

628
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,820
Have you already transferred school?

629
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:17,000
The other day, you wore
a different school uniform.

630
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:19,390
You told me it was a new
standardized design from the school.

631
00:39:19,790 --> 00:39:20,310
I was...

632
00:39:20,310 --> 00:39:21,360
You lied to me, didn't you?

633
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:22,390
No, Mom.

634
00:39:23,040 --> 00:39:25,020
That experimental high school
is really good too.

635
00:39:25,390 --> 00:39:26,020
Song Hang,

636
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,500
you agreed to this?

637
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:32,400
Have you ever thought about
what will happen to his Gaokao?

638
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,240
Mom, you don't have
to worry about my grades.

639
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:35,940
I can still be ranked first over there.

640
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:37,950
This is our son's own decision.

641
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:40,480
He wants to take on
the responsibility of being your child.

642
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,080
I believe he's capable of doing so.

643
00:39:42,430 --> 00:39:43,700
You should respect his decision

644
00:39:43,750 --> 00:39:44,910
and accept his care.

645
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:45,990
It's not a bad thing.

646
00:39:46,140 --> 00:39:47,060
It's bad.

647
00:39:47,060 --> 00:39:48,960
I don't need you all to take care of me!

648
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,460
I'm not completely paralyzed.

649
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:54,020
I don't need you to worry about me.

650
00:39:54,100 --> 00:39:55,500
Alright. That's enough now.

651
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:57,820
You shouldn't get too
worked up in your condition.

652
00:39:59,500 --> 00:40:01,470
It's about mealtime.
I'll go buy some food.

653
00:40:01,980 --> 00:40:03,180
Take good care of your mom.

654
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,980
I don't need you to look after me.

655
00:40:05,180 --> 00:40:06,700
Leave. All of you, just leave!

656
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:27,140
Why are you going through

657
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:28,160
all this formal nonsense?

658
00:40:28,180 --> 00:40:30,180
Do you think Aunt Hao
needs this pot of flowers?

659
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:32,680
If your rhinitis acts up again,
I'd love to see what you'll do.

660
00:40:32,830 --> 00:40:34,760
That's why I told you
to stay away from me.

661
00:40:35,910 --> 00:40:37,220
Song Cong said

662
00:40:37,470 --> 00:40:39,390
Aunt Hao had already
prepared matching scarves

663
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:40,580
for her trip.

664
00:40:40,990 --> 00:40:42,270
With this unexpected situation,

665
00:40:42,430 --> 00:40:43,750
she must be feeling awful.

666
00:40:44,750 --> 00:40:45,430
You boys

667
00:40:45,430 --> 00:40:47,380
just don't understand
a mother's feelings at all.

668
00:40:47,750 --> 00:40:48,700
Yes, you know it.

669
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:50,700
When are you planning
to take it over to her?

670
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:52,100
Right now.

671
00:40:52,180 --> 00:40:54,260
We'll just drop it off
at Song Cong's doorstep.

672
00:40:57,750 --> 00:40:59,020
Do you smell something burning?

673
00:41:00,580 --> 00:41:01,750
Really? No, I don't.

674
00:41:06,420 --> 00:41:08,090
Wait, it is coming
from Aunt Hao's house!

675
00:41:08,790 --> 00:41:09,470
Aunt Hao!

676
00:41:09,620 --> 00:41:11,310
Is anyone home? Open the door!

677
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:13,540
There's so much smoke!

678
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:14,350
I'll make a call.

679
00:41:14,350 --> 00:41:15,020
What could we do?

680
00:41:15,020 --> 00:41:16,180
Song, hurry! Open the door!

681
00:41:16,310 --> 00:41:16,910
Open the door!

682
00:41:16,990 --> 00:41:18,140
Is Aunt Hao home alone?

683
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:19,470
My mom is still inside!

684
00:41:19,500 --> 00:41:20,350
Hao Mei!

685
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:21,500
Aunt Hao!

686
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:22,990
Hao Mei, say something!

687
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:23,990
Aunt Hao!

688
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:25,180
Mom!

689
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:27,830
- Aunt Hao!
- Aunt Hao!

690
00:41:27,990 --> 00:41:28,470
Fire...

691
00:41:28,470 --> 00:41:29,060
Hao Mei!

692
00:41:30,390 --> 00:41:31,270
Are you okay?

693
00:41:31,750 --> 00:41:32,310
Aunt Hao!

694
00:41:32,430 --> 00:41:33,060
Come on!

695
00:41:35,950 --> 00:41:36,540
Aunt Hao!

696
00:41:36,540 --> 00:41:37,910
Mom, are you alright?

697
00:41:37,910 --> 00:41:39,220
Go away, Huan'er.

698
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:40,790
You and Xichi leave.

699
00:41:40,990 --> 00:41:41,750
Go!

700
00:41:43,390 --> 00:41:44,180
Go now!

701
00:41:44,350 --> 00:41:45,870
Aunt Hao, we'll leave first.

702
00:41:46,270 --> 00:41:47,470
Don't touch me.

703
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,700
Did you get burned anywhere?

704
00:41:48,750 --> 00:41:49,310
Are you hurt?

705
00:41:49,310 --> 00:41:50,910
Don't touch me! Don't touch me!

706
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:15,830
It's fine.

707
00:42:17,060 --> 00:42:18,390
I'll take you to change clothes.

708
00:42:19,950 --> 00:42:20,500
It's fine.

709
00:42:20,790 --> 00:42:21,350
It's fine.

710
00:43:30,400 --> 00:43:35,570
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

711
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:42,440
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

712
00:43:44,210 --> 00:43:49,560
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

713
00:43:49,870 --> 00:43:55,360
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

714
00:43:57,950 --> 00:44:02,970
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

715
00:44:04,760 --> 00:44:10,000
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

716
00:44:11,600 --> 00:44:17,020
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

717
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:22,980
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

718
00:44:24,180 --> 00:44:28,140
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

719
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:33,130
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

720
00:44:33,260 --> 00:44:36,690
♪And full of life♪

721
00:44:37,980 --> 00:44:41,440
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

722
00:44:41,440 --> 00:44:46,550
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

723
00:44:46,810 --> 00:44:51,200
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

724
00:44:51,700 --> 00:44:55,600
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

725
00:44:55,600 --> 00:45:00,540
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

726
00:45:00,540 --> 00:45:03,330
♪To know right from wrong♪

727
00:45:05,240 --> 00:45:08,770
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

728
00:45:08,770 --> 00:45:12,020
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

729
00:45:12,180 --> 00:45:17,940
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

730
00:45:18,360 --> 00:45:22,960
♪At just the right time♪
